      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW NATULLO (1) failed to come into contention last start after drifting back at Shepparton, but prior to that won by 2.5 lengths at Warragul (22.87) beating Paw Gusto in a Grade 5 on March 17. Ready to return to form. PAW REVY (3) had a tricky draw but scored by 4.5 lengths (21.93) at Ballarat in Mix 6/7. Failed to fire only run here. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should feature again. PAW WELKES (5) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (22.70) at Warragul. One of the main contenders. SOMERTON MICK (2) has been going along well and was strongly fancied last time but could only manage third (24.66) at this track. Is yet to taste defeat in two starts from this draw.",
